{"tid":2124774,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"721 與英國反恐法","createTime":"2020-07-25T15:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T12:32:20.000Z","uid":278154,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"46ab22fb4687fa6275a15bb56006062e592e931f","tid":2124774,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://x7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-bloody-sunday-min-768x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fx7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-bloody-sunday-min-768x1024.jpg&h=122d567d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知石鏡泉條茂利有無任何類型英國護照，但依家有兩件 721 鄉黑喺英國，果兩條友唔係British Citizen都係UK Resident，以我與英國一啲人嘅研究所得，根據Terrorism Act 2000 Section 63B，其實喺英國果兩件鄉黑係拉得，英國法院有域外法權，甚至石鏡泉揸BNO，都拉得。<br />\n<br />\nTerrorism Act 2000 對 721 有部分管轄權<br />\n<br />\n根據現行 Terrorism Act 2000 Section 63B (1)<br />\n<br />\n(1)If&mdash;(a)a United Kingdom national or a United Kingdom resident does anything outside the United Kingdom as an act of terrorism or for the purposes of terrorism, and<br />\n(b)his action, if done in any part of the United Kingdom, would have constituted an offence listed in subsection (2),<br />\nhe shall be guilty in that part of the United Kingdom of the offence.<br />\n乜嘢叫 United Kingdom national，喺 Section 63A有講，BC同BNO都係 Terrorism Act 63B同63C定義下嘅UK National，而根據 63B，英國國民策劃海外恐襲活動一節 (2)(b)，有呢個條款<br />\n<br />\nan offence under section 4, 16, 18, 20, 21, 22, 23, 24, 28, 29, 30 or 64 of the Offences against the Person Act 1861,<br />\nthe Offences against the Person Act 1861 Section 20，就係ABH，所以英國執法部門可以拉咗果兩件鄉黑去審，林卓廷搜集足夠證據俾Crown Prosecution Service就得，因為 721 已經符合63B嘅英國國民於海外從事恐襲活動。而由於721受害者，應該有人係BNO Holder或BC，所以都符合Section 63C，英國國民於海外受恐襲，所以英國有司法管轄權。 721 大家要搜集好證據，班去如果去英國，立即要求英國政府逮捕呢啲人渣，唔好恐怖分子控制下嘅律政司同香港黑警。<br />\n<br />\n所以周融檔HKGPao，如果有佢哋鼓吹721「教仔」任何證據，請向英國提供，屆時周融唔放棄British Citizen，佢去任何同英國有引渡協議嘅國家，都會被逮捕並送到英國受審，因為石鏡泉同周融，基本上可以用 Terrorism Act 2006 Section 17招呼佢哋，而佢哋干犯係Terrorism Act Section 1同Section 3嘅行為。你估啲黑警同鄉黑去英國好過癮，去英國係坐監都得，呢班人渣敗類。<br />\n<br />\n由於721發生喺Counter Terrorism and Border Security Act 2019生效之後，所以，周融同石鏡泉，只要佢哋仍持有英國國籍，英國都有司法管轄權。<br />\n<br />\nmartinoei 黃世澤:<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/31035/721-%E8%88%87%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F31035%2F721-%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%25B3%2595&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHaDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=ba7b3b3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/31035/721-%E8%88%87%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E6%B3%95</a>"},{"pid":"3c31e60255f321878607da0225748f6df2081b15","tid":2124774,"uid":278154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Id3e8ugFTTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FId3e8ugFTTI&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHaDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=12a15931\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Id3e8ugFTTI</a>"},{"pid":"bfa0ac8c53a3f210c10d36ede504a018c84e11b4","tid":2124774,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0673a6b4e3cec769052f0ec2379ef35abf174483","tid":2124774,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:20:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3aa44f71c6d6d0a54043e7159b189b0bb081beea","tid":2124774,"uid":66392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac8b105e49fbe4c5f1499d80ec4dfd1ada2b7493","tid":2124774,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a5e391b9bb9c441da68053f9e11fd54321d9f26","tid":2124774,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco